  "title": "Surgical Scrub Technician ( Hospital , 5 days work)",
  "description": "<p>Our clients are seeking a skilled and service‑driven Surgical Scrub Technician to support our clinical operations and product utilization in the operating theatre. This role is ideal for someone who thrives at the intersection of clinical excellence, technical precision, and customer-facing collaboration. You will play a key role in ensuring smooth surgical workflows, supporting surgeons with product knowledge, and reinforcing reliability and high‑quality service.<br /><br /><u><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></u><br />• Generate new business through proactive prospecting, promoting medical devices<br />• Conduct persuasive product demonstrations and presentations to surgeons, nurses, and procurement teams<br />• Build strong, long‑term relationships with key decision‑makers across hospitals and specialist clinics<br />• Conduct product evaluations or services in a clinic and hospital setting<br />• Provide post‑sales support to strengthen customer loyalty and drive repeat business<br />• Maintain accurate sales forecasts, pipelines, and activity reports<br /><br /><u><strong>Requirements</strong></u><br />• Diploma/Degree in Nursing, Biomedical Engineering, Life Sciences, or a related field<br />• Experience supporting operating theatres or clinical environments is an advantage<br />• Good communication and interpersonal skills• Strong technical aptitude and willingness to learn<br />• Able to work independently and manage field-based duties<br />• Willing to travel locally; must possess own transport</p><p><u><strong>Perks & Benefits</strong></u><br />• Competitive starting salary<br />• Case & transport allowance (Monthly)<br />• Quarterly performance bonus and AWS• Professional Development – Opportunities for career growth, training, and career development<br />• Medical benefits</p><p>**We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.<br />Your Profile will be kept in our database for more career opportunities.<br />We wish you all the best in your job search.<br /><br />EA personnel: Ong Ping Tiong<br />EA personnel Reg No: R25127323EA <br />License No: 24C2562</p>",
